line_1: And the great boy became a simple wench!

line_1: He swore, and wept, and kick'd the Wench,
line_2: Forgot his Hat, and left the Bench.

line_1: Ye Gods! what Sonnets on a Wench?

line_1: And, sure, I love a pretty wench!
line_2: I sometimes love my thirst to quench,
